{"tid":1090989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"桑拿浴室撞正瑞典休班警 涉毒通緝犯赤裸被捕","createTime":"2019-04-04T00:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T02:13:18.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea75fb3812f51209c63c95844cc39b6107885103","tid":1090989,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:23:54.000Z","msg":"「我們無處不在，即使你見不到我們，我們也與你常在。」瑞典警方在Facebook此句帖文所言非虛，上周五當地一名警員就是在非常私人的地方逮捕通緝犯，那時二人連衣服也沒有穿，肉帛相見&mdash;&mdash;因他們正身處桑拿房內！<br />\n<br />\n瑞典一名休班警員於上月29日在斯德哥爾摩林卡比區（Rinkeby）的桑拿房焗桑拿，他偶然發現旁邊坐着的，正是一名涉嫌販毒、已被判有罪卻正潛逃的通緝犯！該區的副警長博曼（Christoffer Bohman） 表示︰「偶然之下，令人大感驚訝的是，他們在桑拿房內都認得出對方。」<br />\n<br />\n該名警員雖然並非執勤，當時更全身赤裸，但沒因此放過對方，出手將通緝犯緝拿歸案。警方發言人斯卡格林德（Skagerlind）表示︰「該名赤裸的警員，冷靜地對犯人說，他現已被捕。」同僚接到通知後到場帶走犯人，「拘捕的過程很平淡，而犯人沒有掙扎逃走。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》／美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190403/59441313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190403%2F59441313&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5EV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=34a26f8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190403%2F59441313&h=8df86275\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190403/59441313</a>"},{"pid":"0765d01d1425bedd74073ad72320beeb0e2a7b81","tid":1090989,"uid":40470,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:25:06.000Z","msg":"香港休班警就更有效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed778724c572124f7e990e1048be74186027649","tid":1090989,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91daf2974402ce45b03d1d3016e7c1c2ded5bdec","tid":1090989,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:32:15.000Z"